Comparing the 7-day averages of daily confirmed cases from the past 7 days and those from 8-14 days ago, case counts have increased by 9.2%, while daily reported deaths have increased by 4.6%. Similar comparative 7-day averages in the USA show a 63.3% increase in daily reported cases and 45.1% increase in reported deaths.

Impression: The global daily reported over 600 000 newly confirmed infections in the past 24 hours with over 204.74 million cumulative reported cases and over 4.32 million reported deaths. - Mod.UBA]
